data.description: Welcome to this 3 bedroom, 2 bath rancher in Countryside! First thing you will notice as you pull up is the large front yard, on a quiet cul-de-sac. As you walk in the front door, you are greeted with an open floor plan with a living space that includes a wood burning fireplace, a dining area plus bar seating, and a kitchen with stainless steel appliances! Going down the hallway you will find an over-sized storage closet, two secondary bedrooms, and a full bathroom. At the end of the hallway, you have a primary bedroom with an attached bathroom and just wait until you see the size of the walk-in closet! This property not only has a large front yard, but also a large backyard that comes with a storage shed and playset! Buyer to assume the solar panel loan at closing.
